  "title": "Project Manager/Coordinator",
  "description": "<ul><li>Responsible to monitor project progress and schedule</li><li>Preparation of quotation and costing for management approval</li><li>Coordinate with various departments throughout the whole project to ensure smooth flow of schedules and meeting of deadlines</li><li>Attend site meeting, resolve site problems and conduct site inspections</li><li>Evaluate and resolve any discrepancies and problems arising during project</li><li>Leads and manages timely procurement for all permits required by regulatory authorities</li><li>Conduct on-site inspection to ensure the project is completed on schedule.</li><li>Attend project meetings.</li><li>Prepare quotations, costing sheets, and report to the Project Director to proceed with invoicing.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li></ul>",
